  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个FinTech交易流程图，核心是从TransactionQueue开始，先到AuthVault做认证判断。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，AuthVault这里应该是一个菱形判断节点对吧？那认证通过和不通过分别往哪走？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，菱形判断。Yes的话直接进LedgerService做记账；No的话要先走一个中间处理，然后再回到AuthVault重新认证，形成一个循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把TransactionQueue指向AuthVault，然后AuthVault分出Yes和No两条分支。No的分支我暂时连到一个中间节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Yes分支是对的。不过No分支那个中间节点需要命名，就叫FinTech_LedgerService的预处理版本吧，实际上我指的是一个独立的中间服务节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "稍等，您刚才说No分支走到LedgerService，然后循环回到AuthVault。但Yes分支也走到LedgerService，这两个LedgerService是同一个节点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不是同一个。No分支走的是D节点，一个中间处理节点，处理完回到AuthVault重新判断；Yes分支走的是E节点，才是真正的记账服务。让我重新理一下命名。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D",
        "E",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我调整一下：B节点AuthVault判断后，No走向D节点，D再循环回B；Yes走向C节点，C再连到E节点完成最终记账。这样结构就清晰了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "E",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，C和E都是LedgerService相关的节点，C可以看作认证通过后的入口，E是最终执行。这个循环结构表达了until working的意思，直到认证通过才往下走。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C",
        "E",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "流程图画好了，从TransactionQueue进入AuthVault判断，No分支循环重试，Yes分支经过C到达E完成处理。需要我补充可访问性描述吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
